</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/1a3c1de05c2792a1ae076c4c802b3de5feb9bc7a" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.505ex; width:48.784ex; height:6.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \Pr(Y=y_{i})=(1-\pi ){\frac {\lambda ^{y_{i}}e^{-\lambda }}{y_{i}!}},\qquad y_{i}=1,2,3,...}"/></span></dd></dl>
<p>where the outcome variable <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle y_{i}}">
