      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle (1-\pi )\lambda }</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/89efd64f206616b719e024c5a8b43784d9741841" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:8.499ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="(1-\pi )\lambda "/></span> and the variance is <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \lambda (1-\pi )(1+\pi \lambda )}">
