</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/d7e287ec19300140f57e31fd721b79148c33c921" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -3.005ex; width:23.695ex; height:6.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle G(z)=\sum \limits _{n=0}^{\infty }P(Y=n)z^{n}}"/></span> be the <a href="/wiki/Probability_generating_function" class="mw-redirect" title="Probability generating function">probability generating function</a> of <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle y_{i}}">
